Find out from each class which spell is seen as worthless, fairly easy to obtain, semi-tough, and very difficult (as in it only drops off boss mobs). Label them as such.<br>
<br>
I know that shamans have a hard time getting malo, for example. Say Words of Energy drops. The only other class that would need this is a necromancer. However, I have no idea how important it is for a necro to have Thrall of Bones or Quivering Veil of Xarn. Find out and if they're easy enough to obtain, set that drop aside for shamans instead.<br>
<br>
